title: Jay Restaurant Vegetarian Food
description: Small restaurant with a selection of buffet items and a-la-carte menu. Some take-out pre-packaged food is also available. Directions: from the train station, catch the ferry and head west onto Th Naraesuan, after a few minutes walk, you'll come across a small bridge, the restaurant is on your left, just off Th Naraesuan. Roughly between the Main Bus Terminal and The Minivans To Bangkok.
